    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>Yes u can defined any number of classes in single file just you need to provide a different name since all are in same scope. you can access $var using using $this-&gt;var, but you can not access private variables of one class in another class or can not by using object also.
So in your code you can not access $var of </p>
